    <h1>Online bank transfer</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>With the Online bank transfer plugin, you integrate the Klarna payment method Online bank transfer (Klarna Sofort) in your online shop and make it available to your customers. To do so, download the Online bank transfer plugin from the <a href="https://marketplace.plentymarkets.com/en/sofort_5050" target="_blank" rel="noopener">plentyMarketplace</a>&nbsp;<span class="icon "><i class="fa fa-external-link  "></i></span>. You also have to carry out a few basic settings in your plentymarkets system so that the payment methods are activated in your system.<br>
The explanations in this section apply after adding the plugin. You can find more information on adding and installing plugins in the <a href="/en/plugins">Plugins</a> section of the manual.</p>
</div>
<div class="admonitionblock important">
<table>
<tbody><tr>
<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-important" title="Important"></i>
